Goals: Only enter on Valid Signals with Supporting Internals and Conditions
Preparedness: I was up early today, trade was planned
What I Learned: I was thinking of a gap fill from the day prior and entered on break instead of pullback

Goals: Only enter on Valid Signals with Supporting Internals and Conditions
Preparedness: There was a trade on APPL planned that contributed to this, but it did not trigger, I am concerned with moving fast to work and thats not okay

Goals: Only enter on valid signals with supporting internals and conditions
Preparedness: Trade was planned, I was bored, I was wanting market to do something, I thought this could be an outlier
What I Learned: By this time I knew I had a sideways market, flat internals, major financial event the next day, So there was no reason to take a trade, also this trade had already failed once prior so I knew it lacked momentum
Changes Needed: Market wide must be moving, internals cant be flat, do not trade in broadmarket chop, outliers are rare, also do not take trades you already lost without great reasons, number on thing is to protect capital
